Step-1: Install react-redux package
    Provide us functions
Step-2: Make redux store available to react component tree.
    react-redux library provide a component "Provider" for this purpose
    Pass the store to the Provider component as props
Step-3: 
    import useSelector from react-redux to get the state from store
Step-4: 
    import useDispatch function from reat-redux to dipatch actions
